                <h1>Explore the Rich History of Amway: From Startup to Global Leader</h1>
                <p>Amway was founded in 1959 by Jay Van Andel and Rich DeVos in Ada, Michigan. Initially focusing on cleaning products, it quickly evolved into a global leader in direct selling, offering a wide range of health, beauty, and home care items. Amway's innovative business model has empowered millions of entrepreneurs worldwide.</p>
